<div class="about-feature-container">
    <img src="/bryan.webp" alt="bryan looking into bones" />
    <div class="description-container">
        <h2>Your Osteopathic physician</h2>
        <h1>Bryan Lok</h1>
        <p>
            Welcome to the world of healing and wellness with Bryan, an experienced osteopathy
            practitioner. Bryan believes in the body's natural ability to heal itself and uses
            gentle manual therapy techniques to address imbalances and restore optimal function.
            Whether you're experiencing pain, stress, or just looking for a way to enhance your
            overall well-being, Bryan's personalized approach will leave you feeling refreshed,
            rejuvenated and ready to take on the world. Book your appointment today and experience
            the transformative power of osteopathy.
